{"tid":1388413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"由葵涌、天水圍、西灣河三區可見市民對警察嘅民怒","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:17:44.000Z","uid":44055,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"775602f6ea905eb0b18c1883ecbb72f2520624cf","tid":1388413,"uid":44055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"過分使用武力：對前線社工記者以及示威者使用過分武力，明明催淚彈唔可以射向人，有啲仲過期添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n包庇白衫：係人都見到佢哋拎鐵通都話見唔到有人有武器，拍晒膊頭示好，慢慢各散東西放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲委任證淨係識得用嚟影相撐自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得香港人已經受夠，警方一路只係識得壓彈弓，香港人遲早反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日仲同我講水炮車路面測試，我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720093817bc5fce294c53150a3907e3fbe007901","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},{"pid":"7622635a86bc37f02f515d09943d03af7e441d4b","tid":1388413,"uid":44055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠見一隻屌一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6018287f67106a8864d27727dcadd8697b1a8979","tid":1388413,"uid":43152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:44:36.000Z","msg":"我無野講，九點東區法院見<br />\n警犬死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdb99fb0d8360f7c201a3d0b5565251a15762b5","tid":1388413,"uid":264564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"今晚三單嘢，我看到：<br />\n<br />\n1 民怨和群眾力量，街坊團結十分十分重要<br />\n<br />\n2 可能因為昨天港澳辦的話，警察今天更肆無忌憚，追打記者，甚至在人群中拿真的散彈槍對著市民（頭部？至少是水平角度）並已有準備開槍的動作<br />\n<br />\n3 天水圍和西灣河劇本：有人搞抗爭者、搞人者報警屈抗爭者、拉抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n相信3這個劇本會不住發生"},{"pid":"16c0bf443bf4b11cfdb40e90064e6deaaa402cc1","tid":1388413,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73badb93a6dffb85b1e8eaccd4c8e08dff8eb57f","tid":1388413,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720093817bc5fce294c53150a3907e3fbe007901","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"九點，肯定？！！"},{"pid":"12a6c681796174b44700abdeac44eb3b927897c0","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73badb93a6dffb85b1e8eaccd4c8e08dff8eb57f","tid":1388413,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720093817bc5fce294c53150a3907e3fbe007901","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"九點，肯定？！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:37:36.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"22c06ba790c92fe972ea8b1fc27f1fcf20e55bed","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73badb93a6dffb85b1e8eaccd4c8e08dff8eb57f","tid":1388413,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720093817bc5fce294c53150a3907e3fbe007901","tid":1388413,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"九點，肯定？！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYCUMfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb